parameters:
Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Should we
return to Fotizona once?

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: We're only
alive because of our plunder, you bastards! Let's return to
Fotizona!

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: This place
gives me the chills... If you want to go back, just let me
know!
Clea: Understood, I'll come back as soon as possible.

Thief Nora: Ugh... The atmosphere here is really
unpleasant...

Mage Relm: I can feel it too... I can't believe a place like
this exists.

Priestess Sophia: The dwelling of evil spirits... Is this
really such a place?

Tailor Neuro: Kuu! It's getting exciting! I'm expecting
everyone to do their best!
Mage Relm: Sigh... Please don't get in my way, okay?

Pirate Captain Melena: I'm glad you're safe! Hurry and get
on the ship, strange things are appearing!

Pirate Captain Melena: Hurry, hurry! Make sure you can get
the ship ready right away!
Clea: Relm-san! Please get on quickly!

Pirate Captain Melena: Alright, everyone's on board! Set
sail, quickly, let's escape from here!
